HEADWORD: Diffused
<hw>Dif*fused"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Spread abroad;
dispersed; loose; flowing; diffuse.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>It grew to be a widely <qex>diffused</qex> opinion.</q>
<rj><qau>Hawthorne.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Dif*fus"ed*ly</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Dif*fus"ed*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
